title: Titibisco
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, International, Western, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A pleasant curry restaurant which serves Nepalese-style food. Vegan items are dahl, a vegetable curry and some side dishes and other dishes can be made vegan. Please note that samosas contain milk in the pastry. Open for dinner sometimes, so call ahead. Is a short walk from JR Chuo Station.
